candidates.title: Release Jikken v0.6.0
candidates.body: Details can be found in the CHANGELOG.

candidates.title: JK-20: Add support for injecting file data into JKT definition
Feature/jk 138 fix telemetry cross platform
candidates.body: The original telemetry code had a module which failed to compile on MacOSX. We've removed that dependency any built our own mechanism on top of another library which does support MacOS along with Windows and Linux our three main platforms.

candidates.title: update configuration handling, add support for user path config
candidates.body:
Add support for a home folder based configuration file.
Also refactored the code around configs to be a cleaner abstraction into a separate module.
